          "@id": "https://doi.org/10.1074/mcp.TIR120.002155"
        }
      ],
      "sc:description": "The ReactomeGSA packages uses Reactome's online analysis service to perform a multi-omics gene set analysis. The main advantage of this package is, that the retrieved results can be visualized using REACTOME's powerful webapplication.  Since Reactome's analysis service also uses R to perfrom the actual gene set analysis you will get similar results when using the same packages (such as limma and edgeR) locally.  Therefore, if you only require a gene set analysis, different packages are more suited.",
      "sc:license": "MIT",
      "sc:name": "ReactomeGSA",
      "sc:operatingSystem": [
        "Linux",
        "Windows",
        "Mac"
      ],
